Name: Starr OMOP description
Description: For more information about the Starr OMOP database, see https://med.stanford.edu/starr-omop/access.html under OMOP and STARR-OMOP documentation

Name: Starr OMOP specific RIT description
Description:
This is a de-identified version of our OMOP CDM mapping of SHC and LPCH clinical data. It is a set of views that point at the following dataset:

starr_omop_cdm5_deid_2020_06_20

The Clarity datasets from which this mapping was constructed are:

lpch_clarity_2020_06_20
shc_clarity_2020_06_20

Version Information:
CDM Version       : v5.3.1
Vocabulary Version: v5.0 31-MAR-20
